## Language [/adUnits/:id/language/?include=includes]
Get the Language that the AdUnit is using 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the AdUnit to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve the Language for a AdUnit [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            { 
            data : {
                modified_by: null
                name: "English"
                language_code: "EN"
                created_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
                updated_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
                class: "Language"
                version: 1
                modifier: null
                id: 1
                }
            }

## Language [/adUnits/:id/language/:subid/?include=includes]
